Package: objectstore
Title: Object Store Interface
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hugo", "Gruson", , "hugo.gruson+R@normalesup.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A unified interface to object stores, inspired by the Zarr V3 specification.
    A set of S7 classes and methods to interact with object stores, such as the local 
    filesystem or AWS S3.
